    "For efficient and effective annotation, professional annotation tools are available.",
    "These tools offer visual interfaces and interactive features, allowing researchers to effortlessly annotate time, category, and bounding boxes.",
    "Widely used labeling tools include Labelbox, OpenLabeling, and others.",
    "Temporal sliding window: The temporal sliding window technique is often used in action segmentation during dataset preprocessing for temporal action detection.",
    "Its purpose is to detect actions within video sequences."
